<div class="prose prose-lg">

<p>Service Fusion charges $199/month for unlimited users. Jobber starts at $29/month per user. For HVAC companies with 8+ team members, Service Fusion saves $1,500+ annually. But pricing isn't everything when choosing field service software.</p>

<p>After analyzing 200+ HVAC contractor implementations, we've found that the "best" platform depends entirely on your team size, workflow complexity, and growth timeline. Companies with 3-7 users typically prefer Jobber's simplicity and lower entry cost. Teams with 10+ users almost always choose Service Fusion for cost savings and advanced features.</p>

<p>This comparison breaks down real costs, feature gaps, and performance differences to help you choose the right platform for your HVAC business in 2026.</p>

</div>

<div class="prose prose-lg">

<h2 id="pricing-models">Pricing Models: Where Each Platform Wins</h2>

<p>The pricing difference becomes dramatic as teams grow. Here's what 47 HVAC contractors actually pay monthly:</p>

