<p>Service Fusion's pricing includes some hidden costs that contractors discover after signing up. Dispatcher seats cost $49/month each (most HVAC companies need 1-2 dispatchers). Customer portal access costs $1 per customer monthly, which adds $300-800/month for active HVAC customer bases.</p>

<p>Jobber's per-user pricing is transparent but expensive at scale. The Core plan at $29/user lacks job costing and advanced reporting that HVAC contractors need. Most upgrade to Connect ($49/user) or Grow ($79/user) plans, making large teams extremely costly.</p>

<div style="background-color: #e8f4fd; border-left: 4px solid #2563eb; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0;">
<p><strong>Cost Reality Check:</strong> A 15-person HVAC company pays $735/month for Jobber Connect vs $248/month for Service Fusion (including 1 dispatcher). That's $5,844 annual savings with Service Fusion.</p>
